ce:section.ce:para:
As a benchmark reaction, we examined the synthesis of 3-thiocyanato-1H-indole (2a) from indole as model substrate (1a, 0.13 mmol) in THF, as shown in Scheme 3
                      (Table 1
                     ). For this reaction, we used carbon dots (20 wt%) as the catalyst and NH4SCN (3 eq.) as source of thiocyanate. To our satisfaction, compound 2a obtained in 84 % yield by irradiating the reaction mixture with blue LED light (1 W, 465 nm) under air atmosphere for 24 h.
